                    <lb n="3" break="no"/>сѣн</persName> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/evtdict/evt_show/d_05712">цар</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/evtdict/evt_show/d_02958">егда</w> <w lemmaRef="https://histdict.uni-sofia.bg/dictionary/show/d_07916/">прѣѧ</w> 
